edu.iu.dsc.tws.api.tset.sets.batch

Interface BatchTSet<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - tset type
    All Superinterfaces:
    AcceptingData<T>, java.io.Serializable, StoringData<T>, TBase, TSet<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BatchTSetImpl, CachedTSet, CheckpointedTSet, ComputeTSet, PersistedTSet, SourceTSet, StoredTSet

    public interface BatchTSet<T>
extends TSet<T>, AcceptingData<T>, StoringData<T>
    Batch extension of TSet interface. Adds methods related to Batch OperationMode and overrides generic TSet and TLink return type to BatchTSet and BatchTLink in all methods. Also extends the AcceptingData interface because the BatchTSets can accept data from other TSets.
